Just need SBT
http://www.scala-sbt.org/download.html

To run:
$ sbt
Inside sbt:
> compile
> run
Then select the main class to run

As always, with SBT you should have the following line in your repository manager ignore file:
target/

This is a typical Scala single project directory structure:
.
├── build.sbt
├── README
├── src
    └── main
        └── scala
            ├── 1_Hello.scala
            ├── 2_Sub.scala
            ├── 3_Aux.scala
            └── 3_Class.scala
